{
  "type": "normal",
  "rawDescription": "【大堂，夜】",
  "location": "大堂",
  "timeOfDay": "夜",
  "performances": [
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "心理活动"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "小样儿，在我娘面前跟我耍花招，看我怎么收拾你。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "诸位，我娘子酒量不行啊，这杯酒呢，我替她敬诸位一杯。来干了，来来来！为了答谢大家的厚爱，我决定，从今天往后我和我娘子携手并肩，共创美好明天。来！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "来啥啊！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "携手并肩，手啊！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "description": "湘玉牵手"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "来，给大家伙亲一个！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "大庭广众的不太合适吧？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "要的就是大庭广众，要不然怎么叫亲热呢，哼，你不会不敢吧？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "为啥不敢，又不是第一次，昨天晚上还亲了一宿呢！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "众人",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "喔！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "好啊，那就亲吧！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "心理活动"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "翻脸，翻脸，翻脸，快跟我翻脸！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "心理活动"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "事已至此豁出去了，跟他拼了！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "慢着——"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "你咋不躲呢你？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "躲啥呢？亲自己的相公，还犯法吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "不犯法，但他不是你相公。你在撒谎。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "description": "镜头切换黑背景"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "各位观众，昨天晚上，为了防止她偷吃东西，我特意给她抹上了口红 。如果我儿真的亲了她，那在他的嘴上一定会留下痕迹。但事实，并没有。 这足以证明"
        },
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "看着佟湘玉"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "你在撒谎。说，为什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "description": "切回大堂场景"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "我不希望你带他走，他好不容易安定下来，不用再过那种风吹日晒，提心吊胆的日子。这里的生活，虽然平淡，但并不乏味；虽然琐碎，但并不单调。这里的每个人，包括我，都真心诚意地希望展堂能够改过自新，远离那条不归路。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "她说的是真的？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "是真的，娘。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "那你怎么不早告诉我？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "我早就跟您说过了，您死活不信呐。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "对众人"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "这是真的吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "众人",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "是这么回事儿，真的真的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "对众人"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "真是这么回事儿？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "李大嘴",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "真的！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "感动"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "哎，老实说，我行走江湖这么多年，从来就不相信友情，更不相信能有这么多人，不计报酬，不计后果的帮你。今天，我三娘算是开了眼了！来，这杯酒，我敬大家！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "众人",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "来，干干干！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "湘玉妹妹，你的恩情，三娘就是粉身碎骨也无以为报。如果你不嫌弃我儿的话……"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "不嫌弃，不嫌弃！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "就让他给你当外甥，咱俩拜姐妹！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "description": "众人楞"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "怎么？你讨厌我这老太婆？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "不是……"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "那就好，那就好！湘玉以后就是我的亲妹妹了，你们记着，以后你们谁敢欺负她，那就是欺负我。明白了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "众人",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "……明白了，明白了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "还愣着干啥，快叫二姨啊！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "很小声"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "二姨……"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "大点儿声！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "咬着牙"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "二姨！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "哎！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "description": "众人无语"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白三娘",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "湘玉妹妹，以后你外甥的婚事，可就全仰仗着你啦。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "知道了……"
        },
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "心理活动"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "我的神呀，我这造的哪门子的孽哟！"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}